title: Dak Prescott, top QBs, 49ers, and Tom Brady
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, top QBs, 49ers, and Tom Brady
description:
Colin talks about Dallas Cowboys QB Dak Prescott's possible holdout, which QBs should be paid as much as they want, why people shouldn't be criticizing Niners HC Kyle Shanahan's play calling, and the possible outcome for Tom Brady. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Mitchell Schwartz, Peter King, and Bucky Brooks.
